FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://polls.apiblueprint.org/

# nativo

Polls is a simple API allowing consumers to view polls and vote in them.

## Create users [/users]

### Creates a user [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
        
        {
            "email": "halzate93@gmail.com",
            "name": "Héctor Camilo",
            "last_name": "Alzate Ramírez",
            "password": "Password",
            "language": "ES"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "token": "TK_ASDFNKLE23",
            "id": "DB_ASDFNKLE23"
        }


## Retrieve user data [/users/{id}]

### Gets the user data [GET]

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "username": "halzate93",
            "email": "halzate93@gmail.com",
            "name": "Héctor Camilo",
            "last_name": "Alzate Ramírez",
            "points": 100,
            "level": 5
        }

## Login [/login]

### Authenticates the user and retrieves id and session token [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "halzate93",
            "password": "Password"
        }

+ Response 200 (application json)

        {
            "token": "TK_ASDFNKLE23",
            "id": "DB_ASDFNKLE23"
        }

